{"about_the_game":"<p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_01.png?t=1735558582\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Let's roll them bones!</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">In this high-paced, action-packed roguelite you will need to carefully choose a <strong>loadout of spell dice</strong> to beat each dungeon floor.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Pave your way through <strong>15 unique dungeon floors</strong> filled with bloodthirsty enemies! </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_03.png?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/GIF_01_D.gif?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_01.png?t=1735558582\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">What's the deal with dice?</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Each die has 6 sides and possibly up to 6 different spells. Some are good, some are terrible and some will straight up annihilate the enemies (or even yourself).</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Choosing dice that play well against specific dungeon floors is the key to success.</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_03.png?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/SteamPageGIF_New01.gif?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_01.png?t=1735558582\" /></p><h2 class=\"bb_tag\">Interactable spells</h2><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\">Select from hundreds of dice and change how they behave on <strong>Critical rolls</strong>. Go for damage, hit effects, combos or even pure chaos. Spell projectiles vary greatly in stats, effects and even their physics! Throughout the run collect rare modifiers that will further influence spell's behavior. Combine all those choices to annihilate your enemies!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_03.png?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/GIF_03_A.gif?t=1735558582\" /><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_v2_01.png?t=1735558582\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/midbanner_04.png?t=1735558582\" /></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/extras/store_description_transparent_footer_downscaled.png?t=1735558582\" /></p>","background":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/page_bg_generated_v6b.jpg?t=1735558582","background_raw":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/page.bg.jpg?t=1735558582","capsule_image":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/capsule_231x87.jpg?t=1735558582","capsule_imagev5":"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/2527550/capsule_184x69.jpg?t=1735558582","categories":[{"description":"Single-player","id":2},{"description":"Full co